ParentalPartnership_MothersPartners: My mother had three partners; however, I never saw her act romantically with them. my father was one of them, but I've never seen them be affectionate with each other. My second father figure was her second partner but my mother kept her romantic life extremely private, however I could see the love they had for each other based on how they trusted, confided, relied on each other. The third partner my mother had was a long distance relationship that lasted for years but they only met once and I wasn't there. So, again I never saw any romantic gestures between them.
ParentalPartnership_FathersPartners: I know the last serious relationship my father had was my mother but that ended before I was born due to his infidelity and he has lived a bachelor lifestyle my entire life which meant three-four women every month however i never met these women. I know about them because I would see them messaging him when I used his phone to play phone games.
